      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show its age with some cosmetic wear on the interior and minor scratches on the exterior. It has been well-maintained mechanically, though a new owner should expect to address some minor upcoming maintenance items like brake pads or older tires soon. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road but is priced to reflect its used status and high mileage.",
