      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been meticulously preserved. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth, powerful engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly. All maintenance is up to date with full records included, and there are absolutely no leaks, noises, or cosmetic blemishes. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber in such an impeccable state.",
