    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it's time for my absolute pride and joy to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since the day I got her\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed, and treated like a member of the family. She\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking and driving just like she did on the showroom floor. You might find a microscopic mark if you really go looking, but to me, she\u2019s as close to perfect as it gets! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this car is so special.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
