      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 platform, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six that has been meticulously maintained for peak volumetric efficiency. This unit boasts a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue, ensuring the chassis remains true under high-load cornering. The induction note is crisp, indicating perfect valve clearances, while the Getrag 6-speed transmission engages with zero-lash precision. Suspension geometry has been optimized with refreshed bushings to maintain surgical turn-in. This is a concours-level specimen preserved for the discerning purist who demands mechanical transparency and uncompromised power delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
